.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-LOCAL-BALANCE-KURTOSIS-WEEKLY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-local-balance-kurtosis-weekly \- FEAT-2850 channel-local-balance-kurtosis-weekly
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-local-balance-kurtosis-weekly
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the excess kurtosis of local balance (to_us_msat) across all peer channels for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2850).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBlocal_balance_kurtosis_weekly\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
